data.description: Gorgeous Bi-level dream retreat! Welcome home to this 3 bedroom and 3 bathroom property that captures the essence of Montana's tranquil lifestyle with luxurious amenities for comfortable living, with an attached 2 car garage and a huge shop. Conveniently located near Kalispell and situated in 11.62 private acres, surrounded by lush forestry, this is the retreat of your dreams! The main level offers amazingly verticality, great views and timber walls. A private entry foyer, open spacious great room, loft, Floor to ceiling stone fireplace, kitchen, bathroom, additional office/guest room, and primary bedroom with en suite. Lower level offers spacious 2 bedrooms, living space and a bathroom. Contact Dema Weil at 406-607-0205, or your real estate professional. Other features of this property includes; Wood burning stove on the lower level and private entrance, A large 49X59 barn/shop to put all your toys, RV hookups, horse property, chicken coop, garden, mature lush fruit trees. This property is not encumbered by HOA. Security camera in the house.
